title: DDFP: Running back U Super Bowl show
itunes:title: DDFP: Running back U Super Bowl show
description:
Elliot Harrison again joins the boys to decide to break down the NFC side of the best tailback franchise in NFL history and then once and for all, just who is the Running Back U. of the NFL. The answer just might surprise you. Also on the show, Dameshek and Rank talk some college football and start the preliminary discussion of the greatest smells in the world. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
